body:
The Soulstones mod is intended to enhance your Minecraft experience, focusing on your hunt for mobs around the world. Now, when you kill an entity, it has a X% chance of dropping a Soulstone carrying the properties of that entity. Granting pros and cons when using them, discover which Soulstone best fits your style of play and become even more powerful on your journey.

Soulstones added:

- Zombie Soul (5%) - Pros: Enhanced Strength, Enhanced Health - Cons: Constant Hunger;
- Chicken Soul (1%) - Pros: Slow Falling, Egg Spawn - Cons: Reduced Strength;
- Fish Soul (1%) - Pros: Water Breathing, Enhanced Swim Speed - Cons: Reduced Strength;
- Pig Soul (1%-5%) - Pros: Saturation - Cons: Reduced Strength;
- Creeper Soul (5%) - Pros: Press K to Kaboom - Cons: You... are the bomb.
(More Soulstones coming soon)
